sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant NSD
  participant ML as main loop (main.rs)
  participant A as VipAllocator (vip.rs)
  participant R as NscRouter (router.rs)
  participant D as DnsRecords (dns.rs)
  participant PM as ProxyManager (proxy.rs)
  participant L as TcpListener(vip:port)

  Note over ML: T=0 NSC 启动<br/>allocator/router/dns 为空

  NSD->>ML: SSE routing_config<br/>[{site:"office", port:22, domain:"ssh.office.n.ns"},<br/> {site:"office", port:80, ...},<br/> {site:"datacenter", port:5432, ...}]

  rect rgba(240, 249, 255, 0.6)
  note right of ML: 对每个 route 分配 VIP

  ML->>A: allocate("office")
  A-->>ML: 127.11.0.1 (new)
  ML->>R: update_routing → sites_by_name["office"] = {vip:127.11.0.1, domain:"office.n.ns"}<br/>routes[("office",22)] / routes[("office",80)]
  ML->>D: insert("ssh.office.n.ns" → 127.11.0.1)<br/>insert("web.office.n.ns" → 127.11.0.1)

  ML->>A: allocate("office")
  A-->>ML: 127.11.0.1 (idempotent)

  ML->>A: allocate("datacenter")
  A-->>ML: 127.11.0.2 (new)
  ML->>R: sites_by_name["datacenter"] = {vip:127.11.0.2, ...}
  ML->>D: insert("db.datacenter.n.ns" → 127.11.0.2)
  end

  ML->>PM: proxy_mgr.update()
  PM->>L: TcpListener::bind(127.11.0.1:22)
  PM->>L: TcpListener::bind(127.11.0.1:80)
  PM->>L: TcpListener::bind(127.11.0.2:5432)

  Note over ML,L: --- 运行期 ---

  NSD->>ML: SSE dns_config<br/>[{domain:"git.company.com", site:"office"}]
  ML->>D: insert("git.company.com" → 127.11.0.1)<br/>(vip_for_site("office") 已存在)

  NSD->>ML: SSE routing_config (again, with 新 service)<br/>[..., {site:"office", port:443, domain:"https.office.n.ns"}]
  ML->>A: allocate("office") → 127.11.0.1 (idempotent)
  ML->>R: routes[("office",443)] = ...
  ML->>PM: update() → new listener on 127.11.0.1:443
  Note over A,R: VIP 永不回收：<br/>进程退出前所有分配都保留在内存
